definition: we will not elaborate on that (used as pluralis auctoris)
topic/problem for discussion/exam question/subject/to inscribe/to mention/CL:個|个[ge4],道[dao4]

sentences.english: I will not pour out their libations of blood or take up their names on my lips.
sentences.chinese: 他們所澆奠的血我不獻上，我嘴脣也不題別神的名號。

sentences.english: John quit football because he was fed up to the gills with practice.
sentences.chinese: 約翰再也不題足球了，因爲他練球練膩了。
